Lucile Fairbanks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucile_Fairbanks 0 Lucile Fairbanks (1917–1999) was an American actress who appeared in eleven feature films between 1939 and 1942, playing a lead role in A Fugitive from Justice (1940) and Passage from Hong Kong (1941).
